@@$TJvSafeMode
<TITLE TJvSafeMode overview>
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
  TJvSafeMode is a component that enables you to turn on or turn off the monitor.
  
  To use this component you should:
  
  * Drop TJvSafeMode on a form.
  * Call MonitorOn or MontitorOff.
