@@TJvSafeMode
<GROUP TJvSafeMode>
Summary
  Can turn the monitor on and off.
Description
  TJvSafeMode is a wrapper for two lower level function calls, to shut off or turn on the
  display. 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSafeMode.MonitorOff
Summary
  Turns the monitor off.
Description
  Use this procedure to shut down the display.
Parameters
  None.
See Also
  MonitorOn
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSafeMode.MonitorOn
Summary
  Turns the monitor on.
Description
  Use this procedure to turn on the display.
Parameters
  None.
See Also
  MonitorOff